descp2: A `bool`.  Whether to remove "accidental hits" where a sampled class equals one of the target classes.  If set to `True`, this is a "Sampled Logistic" loss instead of NCE, and we are learning to generate log-odds instead of log probabilities.  See our Candidate Sampling Algorithms Reference. Default is   False.
